# Nginx 配置用于 ValgACE Dashboard

ValgACE Dashboard 网页界面的 nginx 配置示例。

## 基本配置

### 方案 1: 独立的虚拟主机

创建文件 `/etc/nginx/sites-available/ace-dashboard`:

```nginx
server {
    listen 80;
    server_name ace-dashboard.local;  # 替换为您的域名或IP

    root /path/to/ValgACE/web-interface;  # dashboard文件路径
    index index.html;

    # 日志记录
    access_log /var/log/nginx/ace-dashboard-access.log;
    error_log /var/log/nginx/ace-dashboard-error.log;

    # 主文件
    location / {
        try_files $uri $uri/ /index.html;
    }

    # 静态文件
    location ~* \.(css|js|png|jpg|jpeg|gif|ico|svg)$ {
        expires 1y;
        # 缓存控制头
        add_header Cache-Control "public, immutable";
    }
    # 代理API请求到Moonraker
    location /server/ {
        proxy_pass http://localhost:7125;
        proxy_http_version 1.1;

        # WebSocket升级头
        proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;
        # 连接升级头
        proxy_set_header Connection "upgrade";
        # 主机头
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        # 真实客户端IP
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
        # 转发客户端IP链
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;
        # 原始协议
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;

        # WebSocket超时
        proxy_read_timeout 86400;
        proxy_send_timeout 86400;
    }

    # 代理WebSocket
    location /websocket {
        proxy_pass http://localhost:7125/websocket;
        proxy_http_version 1.1;

        proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;
        proxy_set_header Connection "upgrade";
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;

        proxy_read_timeout 86400;
        proxy_send_timeout 86400;
    }
}
```

激活配置:

```bash
sudo ln -s /etc/nginx/sites-available/ace-dashboard /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/
sudo nginx -t
sudo systemctl reload nginx
```

### 方案 2: 现有网站的子域名

在现有的nginx配置中添加:

```nginx
server {
    listen 80;
    server_name your-domain.com;

    # ... 现有配置 ...

    # 子域名上的ValgACE Dashboard
    location /ace {
        alias /path/to/ValgACE/web-interface;
        index index.html;
        try_files $uri $uri/ /ace/index.html;
    }

    # 代理API
    location /ace/server/ {
        rewrite ^/ace/server/(.*) /server/$1 break;
        proxy_pass http://localhost:7125;
        proxy_http_version 1.1;

        proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;
        proxy_set_header Connection "upgrade";
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;

        proxy_read_timeout 86400;
        proxy_send_timeout 86400;
    }    
    # 代理WebSocket
    location /ace/websocket {
        rewrite ^/ace/websocket /websocket break;
        proxy_pass http://localhost:7125;
        proxy_http_version 1.1;

        proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;
        proxy_set_header Connection "upgrade";
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;

        proxy_read_timeout 86400;
        proxy_send_timeout 86400;
    }
}
```

## SSL (HTTPS) 配置

### 使用 Let's Encrypt

```nginx
server {
    listen 80;
    server_name ace-dashboard.example.com;

    # 重定向到HTTPS
    return 301 https://$server_name$request_uri;
}

server {
    listen 443 ssl http2;
    server_name ace-dashboard.example.com;

    # SSL证书 (Let's Encrypt)
    ssl_certificate /etc/letsencrypt/live/ace-dashboard.example.com/fullchain.pem;
    ssl_certificate_key /etc/letsencrypt/live/ace-dashboard.example.com/privkey.pem;

    # SSL设置
    ssl_protocols TLSv1.2 TLSv1.3;
    ssl_ciphers HIGH:!aNULL:!MD5;
    ssl_prefer_server_ciphers on;

    root /path/to/ValgACE/web-interface;
    index index.html;

    # 主文件
    location / {
        try_files $uri $uri/ /index.html;
    }

    # 静态文件
    location ~* \.(css|js|png|jpg|jpeg|gif|ico|svg)$ {
        expires 1y;
        add_header Cache-Control "public, immutable";
    }

    # 代理API请求到Moonraker
    location /server/ {
        proxy_pass http://localhost:7125;
        proxy_http_version 1.1;

        proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;
        proxy_set_header Connection "upgrade";
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;
        
        proxy_read_timeout 86400;
        proxy_send_timeout 86400;
    }

    # 代理WebSocket
    location /websocket {
        proxy_pass http://localhost:7125/websocket;
        proxy_http_version 1.1;
        
        proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;
        proxy_set_header Connection "upgrade";
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;
        
        proxy_read_timeout 86400;
        proxy_send_timeout 86400;
    }
}
```

获取 Let's Encrypt 证书：

```bash
sudo certbot --nginx -d ace-dashboard.example.com
```

## 与 Mainsail/Fluidd 集成

如果您已经配置了 Mainsail 或 Fluidd，可以将 dashboard 添加为附加路径：

```nginx
server {
    listen 80;
    server_name printer.local;
    
    # Mainsail/Fluidd
    location / {
        proxy_pass http://localhost:7126;  # 或您的网页界面其他端口
        # ... 代理设置 ...
    }
    
    # ValgACE Dashboard
    location /ace {
        alias /path/to/ValgACE/web-interface;
        index index.html;
        try_files $uri $uri/ /ace/index.html;
    }
    
    # 代理 Moonraker API（如果尚未配置）
    location /server/ {
        proxy_pass http://localhost:7125;
        proxy_http_version 1.1;
        
        proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;
        proxy_set_header Connection "upgrade";
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;
        
        proxy_read_timeout 86400;
        proxy_send_timeout 86400;
    }
    
    # WebSocket
    location /websocket {
        proxy_pass http://localhost:7125/websocket;
        proxy_http_version 1.1;
        
        proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;
        proxy_set_header Connection "upgrade";
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;
        
        proxy_read_timeout 86400;
        proxy_send_timeout 86400;
    }
}
```

## 配置 dashboard 设置

配置 nginx 后，更新 `config/ace-dashboard-config.js`：

```javascript
const ACE_DASHBOARD_CONFIG = {
    // 如果 nginx 代理到 localhost:7125，使用相对路径
    apiBase: window.location.origin,
    
    // 或者如果 Moonraker 在其他主机上明确指定
    // apiBase: 'http://192.168.1.100:7125',
    
    // 其余设置...
};
```

## 安全配置

### 按IP限制访问

```nginx
location / {
    # 仅允许本地网络
    allow 192.168.0.0/16;
    allow 10.0.0.0/8;
    allow 172.16.0.0/12;
    deny all;
    
    try_files $uri $uri/ /index.html;
}
```

### 基本身份验证

```nginx
location / {
    auth_basic "ValgACE Dashboard";
    auth_basic_user_file /etc/nginx/.htpasswd;
    
    try_files $uri $uri/ /index.html;
}
```

创建密码文件：

```bash
sudo htpasswd -c /etc/nginx/.htpasswd username
```

## 检查配置

1. 检查 nginx 语法：
   ```bash
   sudo nginx -t
   ```

2. 重新加载 nginx：
   ```bash
   sudo systemctl reload nginx
   ```

3. 检查可访问性：
   ```bash
   curl http://your-server/index.html
   ```

4. 检查 API：
   ```bash
   curl http://your-server/server/ace/status
   ```

## 故障排除

### 502 Bad Gateway

- 检查 Moonraker 是否正在运行：`systemctl status moonraker`
- 检查 Moonraker 是否在端口 7125 上监听：`netstat -tlnp | grep 7125`
- 检查 nginx 日志：`tail -f /var/log/nginx/error.log`

### WebSocket 无法连接

- 确保正确设置了 `Upgrade` 和 `Connection` 头
- 检查 WebSocket 超时
- 检查 Moonraker 日志是否有错误

### CORS 错误

如果 Moonraker 在其他主机上，在 `moonraker.conf` 中添加：

```ini
[cors_domains]
*.local
*.lan
your-domain.com
*:*
```

## 使用示例

### 通过IP访问

```nginx
server {
    listen 80;
    server_name 192.168.1.100;  # 服务器IP地址
    
    root /home/user/ValgACE/web-interface;
    index index.html;
    
    # ... 其余配置 ...
}
```

### 通过域名访问

```nginx
server {
    listen 80;
    server_name ace.yourdomain.com;
    
    root /var/www/ace-dashboard;
    index index.html;
    
    # ... 其余配置 ...
}
```

